# 🧩 Reactbits Component Installation Guide (Next.js Latest)

## 📌 Overview
Setup installation Reactbits component menggunakan shadcn CLI + GSAP pada Next.js (App Router).

---

## 🎨 Design Standard (Mandatory)

- Background: #303841
- Primary Component: #F6C90E
- Accent: Blue Shades
- Style: Minimalist, High-Contrast, Sharp Borders
- Framework: Tailwind CSS
- Animation Engine: GSAP

---

# 1️⃣ Install GSAP (Required)

npm install gsap

atau

yarn add gsap

---

# 2️⃣ Install Reactbits Component (via shadcn CLI)

Example: Install SplitText (TypeScript + Tailwind)

npx shadcn@latest add @react-bits/SplitText-TS-TW

Command ini akan:
- Menambahkan component ke folder /components
- Inject Tailwind style yang diperlukan
- Support TypeScript

---

# 3️⃣ Usage Example (Client Component Only)

"use client"

import SplitText from "@/components/SplitText"

export default function Hero() {
  return (
    <section className="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-[#303841]">
      <SplitText
        text="Reactbits Animation"
        className="text-4xl font-bold text-[#F6C90E]"
      />
    </section>
  )
}

---

# 4️⃣ Mandatory Rules

- Wajib gunakan "use client"
- Jangan gunakan GSAP di Server Component
- Scope animation per component
- Gunakan Tailwind only
- Ikuti standar warna:
  - Background: #303841
  - Primary: #F6C90E
  - Accent: Blue

---

# ✅ Setup Complete

Reactbits component siap digunakan pada Next.js App Router.